00:08:21.170 --> 00:08:26.369
plus e to the negative 1,
which is also equal to a.

00:08:26.369 --> 00:08:27.910
So what do we have,
a situation here?

00:08:27.910 --> 00:08:31.935
We know that h of
x over the interval

00:08:31.935 --> 00:08:33.809
is less than or equal
to g of x, is less than

00:08:33.809 --> 00:08:36.115
or equal to f of x, which
is less than or equal to a.

00:08:36.115 --> 00:08:40.169
And actually, the only point
where they all equal each other

00:08:40.169 --> 00:08:41.770
is at x is equal to 1.

